Class CreditorBankAccountService.CreditorBankAccountCreateRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gocardless.http.PostRequest<CreditorBankAccount>
      • com.gocardless.services.CreditorBankAccountService.CreditorBankAccountCreateRequest
  • Enclosing class:
    CreditorBankAccountService

    public static final class CreditorBankAccountService.CreditorBankAccountCreateRequest
extends PostRequest<CreditorBankAccount>

    Request class for CreditorBankAccountService.create().

    Creates a new creditor bank account object.

    Bank account details may be supplied using the IBAN (international bank account number) or local details.
